title: CeeLo Green apologizes, wants to return to 'The Voice'
text: > Entertainment CeeLo Green apologizes, wants to return to 'The Voice' In this Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015 photo, CeeLo Green poses for a portrait in Los Angeles. Green says he has grown personally and professionally and wants to return to “The Voice.” “I've talked very possibly about doing ‘The Voice’ again,” Green said in an interview with Associated Press on Wednesday. “So I just kind of put that out there, wishful thinking, kind of willing it. Because I would love to do it again.” (Photo by Casey Curry/Invision/AP)
